    "Lipton, 1990; Miller, 2021).",
    "We can observe that this is the case with ambiguity with medical AI.",
    "The clinicians in those situations seek to understand why AI came to a different conclusion than they did.",
    "They seek an explanation on the background of their own diagnosis and want to know why AI thinks differently.",
    "That creates the context for the given explanation."
